---
import HeroImg from 'src/assets/images/optmatic-insights-feature.jpeg'
---

<div class='relative sm:mb-0 md:mb-10'>
	<div
		class='relative mb-6 h-80 saturate-100 overflow-hidden md:absolute md:right-0 md:h-full md:w-1/3 lg:w-2/5 shadow-md shadow-zinc-950'
	>
		<img class='h-full w-full object-cover' src={HeroImg.src} alt='' />
	</div>
	<div class='relative mx-auto max-w-7xl md:py-24 sm:py-16 lg:py-30'>
		<div class='md:mr-auto md:w-8/12 md:pl-0 md:pr-8 lg:w-7/12 lg:pl-0 lg:pr-0 xl:pl-0'>
			<h1
				class='mt-3 sm:mt-3 md:mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-950 sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl subpixel-antialiased'
			>
				Pragmatic insights to navigate the
				<span
					class='subpixel-antialiased mt-2 pl-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-blue-600'
				>
					digital landscape.
				</span>
			</h1>

			<p class='mt-6 pr-10 leading-snug text-base text-zinc-950'>
				Explore the digital realm with our insights on the latest trends, technologies, and best
				practices in web development & ecommerce.
			</p>
